        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 4. A–F.?Micropora erecta n. sp. A. Group of autozooids (SAMC-A029102) (scale bar = 0.4 mm, magnified x35). B. Autozooids and interzooidal avicularia (SAMC-A029102) (scale bar = 0.2 mm, magnified x75). C. Close-up of the orifice, showing proximal indentations and thickened suboral margin (SAMC-A029102) (scale bar = 0.05 mm, magnified x500). D. Interzooidal avicularia (SAMC-A029102) (scale bar = 0.1 mm, magnified x150). E. Group of ovicelled and non-ovicelled zooids (SAMC-A028821) (scale bar = 0.4 mm, magnified x50). F. Ovicelled zooid (SAMC-A028821) (scale bar = 0.2 mm, magnified x150)." ;
